leads.lead_text: Petioles more or less terete, less than 2 mm wide; mature leaves usually with leaflets
Petioles laterally compressed, 2–8 mm wide; mature leaves often lacking leaflets
Leaflets truly terete, less than 2 mm wide
Leaflets flat, 2 mm or more wide, margins sometimes inrolled giving a terete appearance
Petioles more than 15 mm long; leaflets in 1–4 pairs, glabrous to sparsely hairy
Petioles less than 15 mm long; leaflets in 2–8 pairs, sparsely to densely hairy
Leaflets mostly in 1–2 pairs, linear to narrowly elliptic, mostly more than 5 times longer than wide
Leaflets in 1–6 pairs, linear, elliptic, oblong or obovate, mostly less than 5 times longer than wide
